data.description: OPEN HOUSE this SUNDAY from 12pm-2pm (01/14/2024)  Welcome to this stunning 2-story home located in the desirable Northwest side of San Antonio within the renowned Northside Independent School District. This meticulously maintained property features 4 spacious bedroom, 2.5 bath and solar panels for energy efficiency. Prime located in a gated community, zoned for Northside Independent School District and boasts an open and inviting floor plan with 20 ft high ceilings.This home is perfect for large families, educational professionals, or short term rental investors. Don't miss the opportunity to own a property that combines modern features with a convenient and sought-after location near major highways and amusement parks like Sea World and Fiesta Texas. Schedule a showing today!
